msContents.summary: Copy of the astronomical tables of Ulugh Beg with instructions on calendar conversions, stars and their positions.

supportDesc.extent: 194 foliated leaves : 245 x 155 (205 x 120) mm, bound to 255 x 165 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in nastaʻlīq in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Some diagrams in red; numerous tables in red and black; textblock border-ruled in double red; rubrications in red.

binding.p: Quarter covers with red spine and corners; marbled paper sides with matching marbled paper doublure and endleaves.
